1589static const HashTable JSElementPrototypeTable = { 130, 511, true, JSElement::info(), JSElementPrototypeTableValues, JSElementPrototypeTableIndex };
1590const ClassInfo JSElementPrototype::s_info = { "Element", &Base::s_info, &JSElementPrototypeTable, nullptr, CREATE_METHOD_TABLE(JSElementPrototype) };
1591
1592void JSElementPrototype::finishCreation(VM& vm)
1593{
1594 Base::finishCreation(vm);
1595 reifyStaticProperties(vm, JSElement::info(), JSElementPrototypeTableValues, *this);
1596 JSObject& unscopables = *constructEmptyObject(globalObject()->vm(), globalObject()->nullPrototypeObjectStructure());
1597 unscopables.putDirect(vm, Identifier::fromString(vm, "before"), jsBoolean(true));
1598 unscopables.putDirect(vm, Identifier::fromString(vm, "after"), jsBoolean(true));
1599 unscopables.putDirect(vm, Identifier::fromString(vm, "replaceWith"), jsBoolean(true));
1600 unscopables.putDirect(vm, Identifier::fromString(vm, "remove"), jsBoolean(true));
1601 unscopables.putDirect(vm, Identifier::fromString(vm, "prepend"), jsBoolean(true));
1602 unscopables.putDirect(vm, Identifier::fromString(vm, "append"), jsBoolean(true));
1603 unscopables.putDirect(vm, Identifier::fromString(vm, "replaceChildren"), jsBoolean(true));
1604 unscopables.putDirect(vm, Identifier::fromString(vm, "slot"), jsBoolean(true));
1605 putDirectWithoutTransition(vm, vm.propertyNames->unscopablesSymbol, &unscopables, JSC::PropertyAttribute::DontEnum | JSC::PropertyAttribute::ReadOnly);
1606 JSC_TO_STRING_TAG_WITHOUT_TRANSITION();
1607}

1644JSC_DEFINE_CUSTOM_GETTER(jsElementConstructor, (JSGlobalObject* lexicalGlobalObject, EncodedJSValue thisValue, PropertyName))
1645{
1646 VM& vm = JSC::getVM(lexicalGlobalObject);
1647 auto throwScope = DECLARE_THROW_SCOPE(vm);
1648 auto* prototype = jsDynamicCast<JSElementPrototype*>(vm, JSValue::decode(thisValue));
1649 if (UNLIKELY(!prototype))
1650 return throwVMTypeError(lexicalGlobalObject, throwScope);
1651 return JSValue::encode(JSElement::getConstructor(JSC::getVM(lexicalGlobalObject), prototype->globalObject()));
1652}

1797 RETURN_IF_EXCEPTION(throwScope, false);
1798 return true;

4931
4932JSC::IsoSubspace* JSElement::subspaceForImpl(JSC::VM& vm)
4933{
4934 auto& clientData = *static_cast<JSVMClientData*>(vm.clientData);
4935 auto& spaces = clientData.subspaces();
4936 if (auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForElement.get())
4937 return space;
4938 static_assert(std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSElement> || !JSElement::needsDestruction);
4939 if constexpr (std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSElement>)
4940 spaces.m_subspaceForElement = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.destructibleObjectHeapCellType.get(), JSElement);
4941 else
4942 spaces.m_subspaceForElement = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.cellHeapCellType.get(), JSElement);
4943 auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForElement.get();
4944IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("unreachable-code")
4945IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("tautological-compare")
4946 void (*myVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSElement::visitOutputConstraints;
4947 void (*jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSC::JSCell::visitOutputConstraints;
4948 if (myVisitOutputConstraint != jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)
4949 clientData.outputConstraintSpaces().append(space);
4950IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
4951IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
4952 return space;
4953}
4954
4955void JSElement::analyzeHeap(JSCell* cell, HeapAnalyzer& analyzer)
4956{
4957 auto* thisObject = jsCast<JSElement*>(cell);
4958 analyzer.setWrappedObjectForCell(cell, &thisObject->wrapped());
4959 if (thisObject->scriptExecutionContext())
4960 analyzer.setLabelForCell(cell, "url " + thisObject->scriptExecutionContext()->url().string());
4961 Base::analyzeHeap(cell, analyzer);
4962}

4964Element* JSElement::toWrapped(JSC::VM& vm, JSC::JSValue value)
4965{
4966 if (auto* wrapper = jsDynamicCast<JSElement*>(vm, value))
4967 return &wrapper->wrapped();
4968 return nullptr;
4969}
